    "description": "A structured mesh independence study was conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under VAD operating conditions. Three mesh refinement levels (coarse, medium, fine) were evaluated, with the normalized hemolysis index tracked as the convergence metric across refinement levels.",
