      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence and round-off error contributions to hemolysis QoI must be quantified and shown to be negligible relative to discretization error.",
      "rationale": "Iterative residuals are reported but not linked to QoI error. Round-off error analysis has not been performed. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
