      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD input parameters must be shown to match experimental conditions within documented tolerances for all boundary conditions and fluid properties.",
      "rationale": "Fluid viscosity and density used in CFD differ from experimentally measured values by up to 8%. No formal equivalency mapping between CFD inputs and experimental conditions is documented. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
